rectResponse><setCorrectResponse identifier="RESPONSE_1410376832370"><variable identifier="y" /></setCorrectResponse></templateProcessing><itemBody ><p><p>Gegeben ist die Funktion \(f(x) = x^3\). Geben Sie die Gleichung der Tangente an den Graphen im Punkt \(x_0 = <printedVariable identifier="x_0" />\) an!</p><p>Lösung: \(\qquad t(x) = \)<textEntryInteraction responseIdentifier="RESPONSE_1410376547355" expectedLength="5" />\(x + \)<textEntryInteraction responseIdentifier="RESPONSE_1410376567995" expectedLength="5" /></p><p> </p><p>Diese Tangente schneidet \(f\) in einem weiteren Punkt \(Q(x_Q,y_Q)\). Bestimmen Sie die Koordinaten von \(Q\)!</p><p>\(\qquad\qquad x_Q =\)<textEntryInteraction responseIdentifier="RESPONSE_1410376826822" expectedLength="5" />, \(y_Q =\)<textEntryInteraction responseIdentifier="RESPONSE_1410376832370" expectedLength="5" /></p></p></itemBody><responseProcessing><responseCondition><responseIf><equal toleranceMode="exact"><variable identifier="RESPONSE_1410376547355" /><correct identifier="RESPONSE_1410376547355" /></equal><setOutcomeValue identifier="SCORE"><sum><variable identifier="SCORE" /><baseValue baseType="float">1</baseValue></sum></setOutcomeValue></responseIf></responseCondition><responseCondition><responseIf><not><isNull><variable identifier="RESPONSE_1410376547355" /></isNull></not><setOutcomeValue identifier="FEEDBACKBASIC"><baseValue baseType="identifier">incorrect</baseValue></setOutcomeValue></responseIf></responseCondition><responseCondition><responseIf><equal toleranceMode="exact"><variable identifier="RESPONSE_1410376567995" /><correct identifier="RESPONSE_1410376567995" /></equal><setOutcomeValue identifier="SCORE"><sum><variable identifier="SCORE" /><baseValue baseType="float">1</baseValue></sum></setOutcomeValue></responseIf></responseCondition><responseCondition><responseIf><not><isNull><variable identifier="RESPONSE_1410376567995" /></isNull></not><setOutcomeValue identifier="FEEDBACKBASIC"><baseValue baseType="ident